<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>모두의 옷장 홈</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #fafafa;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .login-container {
            width: 350px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e6e6e6;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            border-radius: 1px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #262626;
        }

        form {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        input[type="text"],
        input[type="password"] {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #fafafa;
            border: 1px solid #dbdbdb;
            padding: 9px 0 7px 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }

        input[type="submit"] {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #3897f0;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .google-login-btn {
            width: 100%;
            background: #DB4437;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .button-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        p {
            color: #262626;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        a {
            color: #3897f0;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
    <script>
        window.onload = function () {
            var urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
            var errorMsg = urlParams.get('error_msg');

            if (errorMsg) {
                alert(errorMsg);
            }

            var message = urlParams.get('message');
            if (message) {
                alert(decodeURIComponent(message));
            }
        }
    </script>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="login-container">
        <h1>👚모두의 옷장👚</h1>

    <p>로그인하여 당신만의 옷에 대한 경험을 소개해주세요.</p>
        <form action="/auth/login3" method="post">
            <input type="text" name="email" placeholder="email" required>
            <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Password" required>
            <input type="submit" value="로그인">
            <div class="button-container">
            <a href="/auth/to-google" class="google-login-btn">Google로 로그인</a>
            </div>
        </form>

        <p>아직 회원이 아니신가요? <a href="/auth/register">회원가입</a></p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
